                     <interp inst="t18300415-48-person580" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was playing at the end of <placeName id="t18300415-48-crimeloc276">Richmond-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18300415-48-crimeloc276" type="placeName" value="Richmond-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18300415-48-crimeloc276" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-48-off273 t18300415-48-crimeloc276"></join>, which is eight or nine yards from the shop, and saw the prisoner run by with the bacon - he threw it down under a chandler's-shop window, pointed with his finger, and called out Stop thief! himself.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I heard Stop thief! cried, and<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183004150040"></xptr>saw a man pass me; I followed, and called Stop thief! a man came and took me to the shop - I have a wife and four children.</p>
